vote.title: Authorize a Lease of Restaurant Space and Facilities in the Terminal Building at Dallas Executive Airport with Creative Bar Concepts, LLC for a term of five years, with two five-year renewal options and a reimbursement for the initial purchase and installation of equipment and furniture - Not to exceed $200,000.00 - Financing: Aviation Fund; Estimated Revenue: Aviation Fund $209,000.00 (over the five-year primary term)
